In July 2002, we opened Publiship Logistics in Australia to further develop our growing business there.

Many publishers and book wholesalers in Australia are hit by expensive unit costs, due to the quantities of each title that are shipped.
Publiship Logistics can assist by arranging consolidation of a number of shipments, in order to reduce costs and improve efficiency.
